        {
            "title": "伊朗戰爭緩解了普丁財政壓力 俄羅斯原油價格升至13年高點",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Argus Media\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"632\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.dfzNw_D0FB.NowLst.eSg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/c280e85d6f0689157659107504d21cc1\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"><span>Argus Media</span></figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 受與伊朗局勢相關的全球油價上漲行情推動，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"俄羅斯\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:俄羅斯;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/俄羅斯\">俄羅斯</a>原油價格升至13年多來的最高水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據Argus Media的數據，俄羅斯的旗艦原油烏拉爾原油4月2日在俄羅斯普裡莫爾斯克港(Primorsk)達到每桶116.05美元。普裡莫爾斯克港是俄羅斯波羅的海沿岸最大的石油出口設施。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一價格不包括運輸成本，幾乎是俄羅斯今年預算所假設的每桶59美元平均價格的兩倍。隨著俄羅斯繼續推進其在烏克蘭的戰爭，意外增加的石油收入正在緩解克里姆林宮的財政壓力。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-cb3f0035-5356-3530-b584-aa56283c1e37-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"632\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/EPMoM1QHkHESGkfNdyrfzA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/68436783858448f308ccba376cd59f8f\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據Argus Media的數據，在俄羅斯黑海港口新羅西斯克(Novorossiysk)，烏拉爾原油周四升至每桶114.45美元。俄羅斯西部港口烏拉爾原油相對於全球基準即期布倫特原油的平均貼水收窄至每桶27.75美元以下，為12月中旬以來最低水平。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">數據顯示，烏拉爾原油運抵印度時，其交易價格相對布倫特原油已轉為升水，且這一升水已從兩周前的每桶3.9美元擴大至每桶6.1美元。目前尚不清楚這種交付價差——即出口價格與交付價格之間的差額——最終是否會歸於俄羅斯。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題War in Iran Drives Russian Oil Prices to a 13-Year High</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%88%B0%E7%88%AD%E7%B7%A9%E8%A7%A3%E4%BA%86%E6%99%AE%E4%B8%81%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B-%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E5%8E%9F%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E5%8D%87%E8%87%B313%E5%B9%B4%E9%AB%98%E9%BB%9E-131629609.html",
