        {
            "title": "美國核心資本品訂單在伊朗戰爭爆發前成長",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Commerce Department\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"728\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/4fuzeKD2oaZbdNXpqOHnDw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/3a87ca8ae93d96311ad9e255b77cea31\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Commerce Department</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國企業設備訂單在2月出現反彈，表明企業在伊朗戰爭爆發前在推進投資計畫。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國商務部周二公佈的數據顯示，扣除飛機的非國防資本品訂單在2月成長0.6%，此前一個月經下修為下降0.4%。彭博調查的經濟學家的預估中值為2月成長0.5%。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"728\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8CukTxbRVoMclLbUdZOAkw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/a065484122eb787bfc259059363eeae4\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">所有耐久財訂單下降1.4%，主要反映飛機訂單減少。波音公司表示，公司2月飛機訂單不及前一個月。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">耐久財報告還顯示，計算機、機動車、金屬和機械訂單均增加。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">經濟學家預計，隨著企業持續加大對人工智能的投入並利用更有利的稅收政策，今年企業投資仍將保持穩健。與此同時，尚不清楚伊朗戰爭對企業的影響。這場衝突已經大幅推高石油及部分其他大宗商品的價格。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-892523d3-e9dc-3a2f-a27f-e5a80426114d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">扣除飛機的非國防資本品出貨成長0.9%。與可能被取消的訂單不同，政府在計算GDP時採用出貨數據。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Core Capital Goods Orders Rise Ahead of Middle East War (2)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Jarrell Dillard.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E8%B3%87%E6%9C%AC%E5%93%81%E8%A8%82%E5%96%AE%E5%9C%A8%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%88%B0%E7%88%AD%E7%88%86%E7%99%BC%E5%89%8D%E6%88%90%E9%95%B7-131248160.html",
